Simplified steem-python with support for these features:
   Make posting,active,owner etc WIF keys from username+password
   Parse WIF or address into key with arbitrary prefixes
   Build op + transaction without overcomplex stuff from steem-python
   Sign unsigned transaction
   Send signed transaction to steemd
   Testnet tools
     Create testnet account and store keys

Test suite
   Full coverage of all of the above 

API endpoints + listener
   As specified in API_DESIGN
